: {"id": 608161, "username": "MRG0", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/MRG0", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/302a/8be1/608161_mini.png?m=1760942115", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/302a/8be1/608161_normal.png?m=1760942115", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/302a/8be1/608161_large.png?m=1760942115", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/302a/8be1/608161_xlarge.png?m=1760942115", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/302a/8be1/608161_xxlarge.png?m=1760942115", "created": 1672197235, "last_modified": 1760942115, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "helloeather", "last_touched": 1776062993, "title": "入职外包，本以为能顺利入职，没想到却要待岗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1205411", "created": 1776046411, "deleted": 0, "content": "在外包总部办完入职第二天我都带上水杯来甲方这里了，结果却带我来了另一个办公楼的一间小办公室，算上\r\n我一共 6 个待岗的。上周有一个后端熬不住跑路了，一个前端入场了，本周剩下的三个后端也入场了。今天问\r\n一下甲方面试的情况，下周才**可能**面试。\r\n\r\n  唯一的好消息可能就是待岗期间全额工资吧\r\n  \r\n  本以为是救命稻草，没想到是另一场消耗", "content_rendered": "<p>在外包总部办完入职第二天我都带上水杯来甲方这里了，结果却带我来了另一个办公楼的一间小办公室，算上\n我一共 6 个待岗的。上周有一个后端熬不住跑路了，一个前端入场了，本周剩下的三个后端也入场了。今天问\n一下甲方面试的情况，下周才<strong>可能</strong>面试。</p>\n<p>唯一的好消息可能就是待岗期间全额工资吧</p>\n<p>本以为是救命稻草，没想到是另一场消耗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1776047869, "replies": 60, "id": 1205411}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_large.png?m=1751415489", "name": "ios", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_normal.png?m=1751415489", "title": "iOS", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/ios", "topics": 4399, "footer": "", "header": "运行于 Apple 移动设备上的操作系统。", "title_alternative": "iOS", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/069d/3bb0/580_mini.png?m=1751415489", "stars": 1180, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 580, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 472538, "username": "Fike", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Fike", "website": "", "twitter": "", "ps